{"title":"一句话书评","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":1,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句话书评"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《诗经》——先民的歌唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《左传》——诸侯争盟记。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《山海经》——神话的故乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《楚辞》——泽畔的悲歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《孙子兵法》——不朽的战争艺术。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《盐铁论》——汉代财经大辩论。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《天工开物》——科技的百科书。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《老子》——生命的大智慧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《墨子》——救世的苦行者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《史记》——历史的长城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《庄子》——哲学的天籁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《荀子》——人性的批判。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《战国策》——隽永的说辞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《资治通鉴》——帝王的镜子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《颜氏家训》——一位父亲的叮咛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《老残游记》——帝国的最后一瞥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《聊斋志异》——瓜棚下的怪谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《三国演义》——龙争虎斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《红楼梦》——失去的大观园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《儒林外史》——书生现形记。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自《青年文摘》）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}